org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators.async.queue

接口 StreamElementQueue

  • 所有已知实现类:
    OrderedStreamElementQueue, UnorderedStreamElementQueue

    @Internal
public interface StreamElementQueue
    Interface for blocking stream element queues for the AsyncWaitOperator.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      boolean isEmpty()
      True if the queue is empty; otherwise false.
      AsyncResult peekBlockingly()
      Peek at the head of the queue and return the first completed AsyncResult.
      AsyncResult poll()
      Poll the first completed AsyncResult from the head of this queue.
      <T> void put(StreamElementQueueEntry<T> streamElementQueueEntry)
      Put the given element in the queue if capacity is left.
      int size()
      Return the size of the queue.
      <T> boolean tryPut(StreamElementQueueEntry<T> streamElementQueueEntry)
      Try to put the given element in the queue.
      java.util.Collection<StreamElementQueueEntry<?>> values()
      Return the collection of StreamElementQueueEntry currently contained in this queue.

    • 方法详细资料

      • put

        <T> void put(StreamElementQueueEntry<T> streamElementQueueEntry)
      throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Put the given element in the queue if capacity is left. If not, then block until this is the case.
        类型参数:
        T - Type of the entries future value
        参数:
        streamElementQueueEntry - to be put into the queue
        抛出:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - if the calling thread has been interrupted while waiting to insert the given element

      • tryPut

        <T> boolean tryPut(StreamElementQueueEntry<T> streamElementQueueEntry)
            throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Try to put the given element in the queue. This operation succeeds if the queue has capacity left and fails if the queue is full.
        类型参数:
        T - Type of the entries future value
        参数:
        streamElementQueueEntry - to be inserted
        返回:
        True if the entry could be inserted; otherwise false
        抛出:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - if the calling thread has been interrupted while waiting to insert the given element

      • peekBlockingly

        AsyncResult peekBlockingly()
                    throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Peek at the head of the queue and return the first completed AsyncResult. This operation is a blocking operation and only returns once a completed async result has been found.
        返回:
        Completed AsyncResult
        抛出:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - if the current thread has been interrupted while waiting for a completed async result.

      • poll

        AsyncResult poll()
          throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Poll the first completed AsyncResult from the head of this queue. This operation is blocking and only returns once a completed async result has been found.
        返回:
        Completed AsyncResult which has been removed from the queue
        抛出:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - if the current thread has been interrupted while waiting for a completed async result.

      • values

        java.util.Collection<StreamElementQueueEntry<?>> values()
                                                 throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        Return the collection of StreamElementQueueEntry currently contained in this queue.
        返回:
        Collection of currently contained StreamElementQueueEntry.
        抛出:
        java.lang.InterruptedException - if the current thread has been interrupted while retrieving the stream element queue entries of this queue.

      • isEmpty

        boolean isEmpty()
        True if the queue is empty; otherwise false.
        返回:
        True if the queue is empty; otherwise false.

      • size

        int size()
        Return the size of the queue.
        返回:
        The number of elements contained in this queue.
